column303:
Ataparyant ya gavat mahila arakshan alela nahi.
January 2020 mdhe thet janatetun sarpanch nivdun ala. Ani nantar nivadnuk ayogane thet janatetun sarpanch pad radd kele.mag tyanantar September 2021 mdhe sadasya madhun chalu sarpanchacha binvirodh nivad karanyat ala.
Grampanchayat durgam bhagat aslyane gramsevak roj yet nahi.

column221: 15 vitt ayog, sc. St. Yojana, jansuvidha, amdar nidhi, sthanik vikas nidhi

column245: Well facilities [or health facilities/ drinking water infrastructure]
column303: Ya gavat anusuchit jamati loksankhya 100% ahe, etar kontehi jat nahi.
Gramsevakana ya gavacha padbhar sambhalun fakt 2 mahine jhale. Gavababatit kahich mahiti nahi. Kahi prashnanche uttar karmachari dile.
Sarpanch swatache kam swata karat nahi, sarpanch majuri kamasathi bahergavi jat asato, mhanun majhi sarpanch prabhavipane sarpanchachya chair var basun kam pahato.
Sarpanch ani upsarpanch doghehi active nhi
